Package: testall
Title: A test package to sanity check argument dependencies within selfwritten
       functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Andre", "Bleier", email = "andrebleier@live.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package tests the outcome of a function under varying argument
             types. The user can create a grid of scenarios to be tested, while the
             function returns a summary of all scenarios and possible errors.
Depends: R (>= 3.5), purrr, dplyr, reshape2, rlist
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
